HEADWORD: Chemigraphy
<hw>Che*mig"ra*phy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Chemical</ets> + <ets>-graphy</ets>.]</ety> <def>Any
mechanical engraving process depending upon chemical action; specif., a
process of zinc etching not employing photography.</def> --
